    "feat": {
        "name": "Play to the Crowd",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You have a knack for knowing just how to manipulate groups by saying exactly what needs to be said. When you Lie in a public area in front of a crowd, you can gauge the reactions of the crowd as you speak to know how your Lie is working, and Lie loses its secret trait. You gain the Reactive Falsehood reaction.  \n  \n**Reactive Falsehood** (fortune)",
        "level": 12,
        "traits": [
