        "prerequisite": "*Dandy Dedication*; master in *Deception*",
        "frequency": "once per hour",
        "trigger": "You fail to Lie to a creature in public; Effect As your target sees through your lie, you spin your falsehood in a way that utilizes the crowd\u2019s reaction to bolster believability. Re-roll your Deception check to Lie with a +2 status bonus and use this check\u2019s result as the actual result to Lie.",
